          architectural-analysis services.
        </li>
        <li>
          You may <b>not</b> reverse-engineer, parse, scrape, stockpile, or
          otherwise bulk-download the Dataset for the purpose of creating
          competitive products or services. Browsing
          <a href="https://sites.fractune.dk">sites.fractune.dk</a> is
          permitted for individual lookups, not bulk export.
        </li>
        <li>
          You may <b>not</b> use the Dataset, or any output of the Fractune
          analysis pipeline, to train, refine, or generate artificial
          intelligence (AI) or machine learning models without prior written
          permission from Fractune.
        </li>
        <li>
          You may <b>not</b> use the Dataset to attempt to identify,
